          "explanation": "Windshield wiper syndrome is seen due to malposition of lens: IOL movement to and fro with the movement of head Complications due to Intra ocular lens - UGH Syndrome : Uveitis , glaucoma, Hyphaema syndrome - Sunrise Syndrome (superior subluxation of IOL) - Sunset syndrome (inferior subluxation of IOL) - Lost lens syndrome (Dislocation of lens) - Windshield wiper syndrome",
