          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Parenchymatous xerosis :- Trachoma, Diphtheria conjunctivitis, SJS, Pemphigus, Thermal/ chemical/ radiational burn, lagophthalmos due to symblepharon.\nEpithelial xerosis:- Vitamin A deficiency (Xerophthalmia)."
