          "explanation": "Diagnosis of glaucoma field defect is best done by Humphrey field perimeter(Gold standard). EARLIEST VISUAL FEILD DEFECT- PARA CENTRAL SCOTOMA Visual feild is defined as area if space visible to human eye without moving the eye fro central target. Rule of thumb:Earliest visual field defect in glaucoma always begin from close to center i.e Paracentral > Bjerrum > Generalized constriction. Extra edge: In Glaucoma, Temporal visual field is the last visual field to be affected.",
