          "explanation": "Direct ophthalmoscope has the following advantages over indirect ophthalmoscope: easily poable, viual and erect image and larger magnification (15X).Indirect ophthalmoscope has the following advantages: binocularity, higher field of view and the presence of teaching mirror.",
