          "id": "medmcqa-614a0212-2a5d-4b91-8c2b-8508c0efad48",
          "text": "A 7 year old boy living in a low socio-economic background presenting with ocular complaints, was found to have nodules on the bulbar conjunctiva near the limbus. Phlyctenular conjunctivitis is diagnosed. Regarding phlyctenular conjunctivitis TRUE is:",
